peopleAlsoAsk.question: Do old rotary phones have any value?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet:
Yes, some rotary phones are valuable. Collectors often seek pieces in colors other than black, brown, white and beige, so phones that are blue, green, yellow, red, pink or purple may be worth more. The maker, age and condition will also impact the value.
Dec 22, 2022
